snippet.title: Desert Island Fishing
snippet.description:
From the creators of The Last Vikings (a google indie GOTY 2016), Tiny Dice Dungeon and some other games that we can't be bothered to write down, comes "DESERT ISLAND FISHING".

It's not strictly a fishing game, there are islands to be discovered, mysteries to be uncovered, and more secrets than you ever thought possible! 

A most epic fishing adventure...coming soon
